org.pragmaticminds.crunch.api.values

Class UntypedValues

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pragmaticminds.crunch.api.values.UntypedValues
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, CRecord, MRecord

    public class UntypedValues
extends Object
implements MRecord
    Class for Transporting "UntypedValues" e.g. over Kafka. If one has MRecords with many values and only a small subset is frequently used it is way more efficint to use this class than TypedValues.
    Author:
    julian, Erwin Wagasow Created by julian on 23.10.17 Modified by Erwin Wagasow on 06.09.2018
    See Also:
    TypedValues, Serialized Form
